oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Harold Wells Job No. 37414
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Accounting; Hatch Show Print (Firm); Lynn, Gerrie;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Invoice (No. 1961) for an order placed by Harold Wells for 50 two color jumbos for performances at Kenny's Club by Chuck Dallas on October 1 and 2, Chuck and Arlene Edwards on October 8 and 29, Bill Madewell on October 9 and 30, Gerrie Lynn on October 15 and 6, and Bobby Sisco on October 22 and 23. Receipt indicates the agreed price, quantity, shipping method, and a description of the posters.
